</p>

<break time="5000ms"/>

<!-- Phase 2: Natural Breath Observation (4 mins) -->
<p>
<s>Before we begin any technique, simply observe your natural breath.</s>
</p>

<break time="3500ms"/>

<p>
<s>Don't change anything yet.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Just watch.</s>
</p>

<break time="4000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Notice where your breath moves in your body.</s>
<break time="3500ms"/>
<s>Does your chest rise?</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Does your belly expand?</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Do your ribs move outward?</s>
</p>

<break time="4500ms"/>

<p>
<s>There is no right or wrong here.</s>
<break time="2500ms"/>
<s>Only observation.</s>
</p>

<break time="4000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Notice the rhythm.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Is it fast or slow?</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Shallow or deep?</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Smooth or uneven?</s>
</p>

<break time="4500ms"/>

<p>
<s>As you watch your breath, something interesting happens.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>The act of watching begins to slow it down.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Begins to deepen it.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>This is natural.</s>
<break time="2500ms"/>
<s>Allow it.</s>
</p>

<break time="5000ms"/>

<p>
<s>The breath is the bridge between your conscious and unconscious mind.</s>
<break time="3500ms"/>
<s>It is the only function of your body that operates both automatically and voluntarily.</s>
</p>

<break time="4000ms"/>

<p>
<s>When you take control of your breath, you take the wheel of your nervous system.</s>
</p>

<break time="5000ms"/>

<!-- Phase 3: Diaphragmatic Breathing (4 mins) -->
<p>
<s>Now let's deepen your breath with diaphragmatic breathing.</s>
</p>

<break time="3000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Place one hand on your chest.</s>
<break time="2500ms"/>
<s>Place your other hand on your belly, just below your navel.</s>
</p>

<break time="3500ms"/>

<p>
<s>As you inhale, focus on pushing your belly hand outward.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Your chest hand should stay relatively still.</s>
</p>

<break time="3500ms"/>

<p>
<s>Inhale now.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Fill your belly like a balloon.</s>
</p>

<break time="5000ms"/>

<p>
<s>And exhale.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Let your belly fall.</s>
</p>

<break time="5000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Again.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Inhale.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Belly rises.</s>
</p>

<break time="5000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Exhale.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Belly falls.</s>
</p>

<break time="5000ms"/>

<p>
<s>This is the breath of babies.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>The breath you were born knowing.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Somewhere along the way, you forgot.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Now you are remembering.</s>
</p>

<break time="4500ms"/>

<p>
<s>Continue breathing this way.</s>
<break time="2500ms"/>
