<break time="2500ms"/>
<s>Into your belly.</s>
</p>

<break time="5000ms"/>

<p>
<s>With each breath, your nervous system calms.</s>
<break time="3500ms"/>
<s>Your heart rate slows.</s>
<break time="3500ms"/>
<s>Your body softens.</s>
</p>

<break time="5000ms"/>

