<!-- Phase 6: The Breath of Light (4 mins) -->
<p>
<s>Now we enter the deeper practice.</s>
<break time="2500ms"/>
<s>The breath of light.</s>
</p>

<break time="4000ms"/>

<p>
<s>With each inhale, imagine you are breathing in pure, radiant light.</s>
<break time="3500ms"/>
